  "text": "Crystallization and Structure Determination of cSrc-B1. Fragment B1 was co-crystallized with cSrc using conditions similar to those previously reported by Michalczyk et al. [CITATION_1] Diffraction data of the cSrc-B1 complex crystals were collected at the PX10SA beamline of the Swiss Light Source (PSI, Villingen, Switzerland) to a resolution of 2.5 Å, using wavelengths close to 1 Å. The data set was processed and refined as described previously. [CITATION_2] Detailed data, refinement, and Ramachandran statistics are provided in Supplementary Table S5. ■ ASSOCIATED CONTENT",
